{"title":"奔腾吧，黄河……——献给我的祖国","authors":["易仁寰"],"dates":[{"year":1995,"month":10,"day":2}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"奔腾吧，黄河……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"——献给我的祖国"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"易仁寰"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你是伟岸的雄性——黄河"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"惊涛裂岸，气势磅礴"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"多少壮士饮马"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"多少豪杰逐波"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一切逆子外寇"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"都被埋葬于急流漩涡"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你的每一座浪峰，都是高耸"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"的城垛　你的河床涌动着激昂的旋律"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"涌动着排山倒海的求索"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"百折不回的走向"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"澎湃着爱的呼唤，心的呐喊，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"力的聚合……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"黄河，你赋予中华民族"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"金黄的肤色——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那是成熟的颜色"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"收获的颜色"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"土地的颜色"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们珍重这肤色"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"用它绘就谷穗、齿轮、星座"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"和龙的传说……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"奔腾吧，黄河"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"九曲之弯的黄河——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"奔腾，才是你的生命"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"曲折，磨炼你的性格"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"曲折也是一种美"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一种运动和劳作"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"弯曲的黄河是一张巨弓"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"正射出无坚不摧的拚搏……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你能容纳百川"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"所以聚成大河"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你若背弃土地"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"势必酿成洪祸"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你与长江、珠江结伴远行"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你与延河、大渡同一脉络……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你不拒绝亚马孙河、尼罗河"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"密西西比河的友好来访"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你还记得伏尔加河"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那逝去的融融清波……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"黄河大合唱"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们民族永恒的战歌"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"谁若玷污黄河"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"谁若肢解黄河"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那么，五千四百公里长啸"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"就会把一切噪音淹没"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"呵，黄河"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你魅力四射"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"光芒四射"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"绿色的淡装"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"已嵌上明珠颗颗"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在你秀丽的肩窝"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"栖着宁静的和平鸽……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"呵，黄河"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你巨浪拍天"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"征帆不落"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"载涛声八万里"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"携昆仑十亿座"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一路浩歌，一路凯歌——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"从高原俯冲，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"汇入大海的壮阔……"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":4,"page_end":4}